description:
World of Tanks: Battlegrounds - All the elements of the board game have been designed and produced with utmost precision, reflecting the computer game's world in an extremely realistic manner. This makes all the battles on the table nothing short of those that rage in the virtual reality. In both cases, the game is based on three common elements: locations, tanks and tactical battle. The board gameplay is made even more realistic thanks to the pictures of tanks and locations being identical to those in the &ldquo;World of Tanks&rdquo; computer game.

The game offers four gameplay options:

     basic (battle) &ndash; uncovered memory type &ndash; on their way to victory, players conquer locations and fight tank battles between each other;
     team &ndash; for pairs (this option can be played by two or four players);
     family &ndash; covered memory type &ndash; players move through the board with their tanks, looking for location pairs;
     solo &ndash; a race between the game and the player to conquer more locations.

